      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[计算机网络] 基础知识</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="一次访问">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e8%ae%bf%e9%97%ae"></a>
一次访问
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">你的软件
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">你的电脑网络配置
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">DNS：把域名翻译成 IP
