    <item>
      <title>[工具] OpenCode</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/opencode/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/opencode/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[工具] OpenCode</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="规则">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%a7%84%e5%88%99"></a>
规则
</h1><h3 id="1-项目级规则">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e9%a1%b9%e7%9b%ae%e7%ba%a7%e8%a7%84%e5%88%99"></a>
1. 项目级规则
</h3><p>在项目根目录放置一个 <code>AGENTS.md</code> 文件</p>
<h3 id="3-全局规则">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#3-%e5%85%a8%e5%b1%80%e8%a7%84%e5%88%99"></a>
3. 全局规则
</h3><p>在 <code>~/.config/opencode/AGENTS.md</code> 文件中设置全局规则</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">你始终用中文回复。你要开始进行操作时，需要先询问我是否开始。
</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id="常用命令">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%b8%b8%e7%94%a8%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4"></a>
常用命令
</h1><p>读取项目</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">/init
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>压缩上下文</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">/compact
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>选择model</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">/models
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>添加model</p>
